{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.320", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrter Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.400", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kolleginnen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.360", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Verehrte Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "13.360", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jedes gerichtliche Verfahren kostet Zeit und Geld, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "13.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.600", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und weil Zeit Geld ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.960", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kostet es umso mehr, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.880", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "je l\u00e4nger ein Verfahren dauert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "23.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb ist nur schnelles Recht auch gutes Recht."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "23.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.680", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bei den Verwaltungsgerichten hat sich die Verfahrensdauer in den letzten Jahren erheblich gesteigert. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "38.440", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Zust\u00e4ndigkeitsbereich des Verwaltungsgerichtes Berlin dauert ein Verfahren bis zur Rechtskraft der Entscheidung im Schnitt um die 20\u00a0Monate, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "38.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.560", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also fast zwei Jahre kostbare Zeit. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.400", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dies betrifft nicht nur Asylverfahren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.160", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sondern auch jedes andere verwaltungsgerichtliche Verfahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "47.240", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jede Familie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "47.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.160", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die gerne ein Eigenheim bauen m\u00f6chte, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.680", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sich aber in einem \u00f6ffentlich-rechtlichen Bauprozess befindet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "57.240", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss die Dauer des Verfahrens ebenfalls einkalkulieren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "57.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.080", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die L\u00f6sung des Problems k\u00f6nnte nun sein\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.240", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der Kollege Seif hat es geschildert\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "63.240", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "zu sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "63.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.520", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann stellen wir mehr Richter ein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.120", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber ein Stellenaufwuchs im \u00f6ffentlichen Sektor ist zum Ersten nicht besonders originell und zum Zweiten auch teuer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "73.920", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Hinzu kommt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "73.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "76.400", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass diese Stellen auch dann noch bedient werden m\u00fcssen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "76.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "81.040", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn hoffentlich irgendwann die Arbeitsbelastung der Gerichte wieder sinkt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "81.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.080", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der L\u00f6sungsansatz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "84.720", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "den die Gr\u00fcnen heute mit ihrem Gesetzentwurf vorgelegt haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "84.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.040", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist eigentlich der viel schlauere und der intelligentere."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.320", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Antrag sieht vor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.040", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Effizienzreserven gehoben und Verfahrensabl\u00e4ufe hinsichtlich einer m\u00f6glichen Verbesserung gepr\u00fcft werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.360", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich finde, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "95.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "98.920", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist eine sehr nachdenkenswerte Idee. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "98.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "102.600", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zun\u00e4chst einmal dauern die Verfahren dann l\u00e4nger\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "102.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "104.240", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Seif, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "104.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "105.480", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "da haben Sie recht\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "105.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "109.480", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil weitere Rechtsmittelm\u00f6glichkeiten gegeben werden; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "109.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.800", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "man muss aber noch einen zweiten Blick auf den Vorschlag der Gr\u00fcnen werfen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.920", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man muss fragen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.480", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was passiert im zweiten Schritt? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "125.520", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Zahl der offenen Antr\u00e4ge beim Bundesamt f\u00fcr Migration und Fl\u00fcchtlinge ist inzwischen auf unter 100\u00a0000 gefallen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "125.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.920", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele F\u00e4lle landen aber woanders, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.160", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "n\u00e4mlich bei den Verwaltungsgerichten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.160", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Momentan sind bundesweit 320\u00a0000\u00a0F\u00e4lle in Bearbeitung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.840", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Gerichte m\u00fcssen im Augenblick jedem Einzelfall nachgehen und die Verfolgungssituation in jeder Provinz, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.680", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "in jeder Region f\u00fcr jede Bev\u00f6lkerungsgruppe eines Landes pr\u00fcfen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "156.760", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil es nur diese eine Tatsacheninstanz und eben keine obergerichtlichen Entscheidungen dazu gibt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "156.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.440", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir haben in \u00a7\u00a078 Absatz\u00a06 Asylgesetz zwar die M\u00f6glichkeit der Sprungrevision zum Bundesverwaltungsgericht; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "166.320", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber das ist eine reine Rechtspr\u00fcfungsinstanz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "166.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "168.760", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dort werden die Tatsachen nicht \u00fcberpr\u00fcft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "168.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "169.240", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "169.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.000", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben eine zersplitterte Rechtsprechung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "174.000", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es bleibt dabei, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "174.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "179.000", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass jedes Gericht die Tatsachen noch einmal pr\u00fcfen muss, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "179.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.320", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und das braucht Zeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "191.000", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn nun das Bundesverwaltungsgericht als neue Tatsacheninstanz auch allgemeinverbindlich Tatsachen \u00fcberpr\u00fcfen und feststellen kann, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "191.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.040", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann entlastet das im Endeffekt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "194.400", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "also im zweiten Schritt, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "194.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "196.000", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wenn das Verfahren durchschritten ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "196.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.040", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nat\u00fcrlich die Gerichtsbarkeit in der ersten Instanz. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "209.320", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hilft dem Bundesamt f\u00fcr Migration und Fl\u00fcchtlinge und den Verwaltungsgerichten in erster Instanz bei ihren Entscheidungen und f\u00fchrt im Endeffekt dazu, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "209.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "211.520", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Verfahren effizienter und schneller werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "211.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "214.600", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00dcbrigens erfolgen dann auch die Ablehnungen schneller. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "214.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.840", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Verfahren werden berechenbarer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "217.360", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Man wei\u00df, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "217.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "218.600", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was einen erwartet. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "218.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "220.600", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Au\u00dferdem werden die Verfahren einheitlicher. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "220.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.000", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das hei\u00dft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "223.840", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir bekommen am Ende schnellere Entscheidungsprozesse, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "223.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "225.560", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "schnellere Verfahren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "225.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.440", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann haben die Gerichte auch wieder mehr Zeit und mehr Luft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.480", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann haben sie die H\u00e4nde frei f\u00fcr den Prozess der Familie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "235.320", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die gerne endlich den ersten Spatenstich f\u00fcr ihr Familienheim machen w\u00fcrde."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "235.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.160", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist ein schlauer Antrag. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.600", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Er k\u00f6nnte auch von uns sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.080", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege Thomae, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.120", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ich enthalte mich hierzu jeden Kommentars."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "248.600", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als N\u00e4chste spricht zu uns die Kollegin G\u00f6kay Akbulut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "248.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.080", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich weise darauf hin, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.000", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass das ihre erste Bundestagsrede ist."
   ]
  }
 ]
}